{{Project Page}}
=Description=
[https://nationalzoo.si.edu/migratory-birds/bird-friendly-coffee Bird Friendly Coffee website]

When you drink Bird Friendly¬Æ certified coffee, you brew a more biodiverse, sustainable world. Using Smithsonian conservation science, the Bird Friendly gold standard does more than other eco-friendly seals to protect habitat, which is often destroyed to make way for coffee growing. Bird Friendly coffees come from farms using a combination of foliage cover, tree height and biodiversity to provide quality habitat for birds and other wildlife. 

The Bird Friendly¬Æ program aims to protect the most quality habitat from the threat of deforestation under the Bird Friendly seal. Look for the Bird Friendly seal ‚Äî the gold standard in eco-friendly, organic farming ‚Äî from [https://nationalzoo.si.edu/migratory-birds/where-buy-bird-friendly-coffee certified Bird Friendly roasters].


